    <h2 class="u-heading-size-medium u-heading-style-normal">12. Fridja F1500 High Pressure Clothes Steamer</h2><p><a class="ck-custom-link" href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/Fridja-Clothes-Steamer-Matte-Black/dp/B082SXQ89R/ref&#61;sr_1_3?tag&#61;telegraphaffiliate-21&amp;ascsubtag&#61;customid-21" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">189.99, Amazon</a></p><p><strong>Best upright clothes steamer</strong></p><p><strong>We like: </strong>how powerful the steam is</p><p><strong>We dont like: </strong>it takes a while to heat up</p>
  
</div>
</div>
<figure itemscope="true" data-test="article-body-image" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" data-js="article-body-image" itemprop="image" class="article-body-image section">





	

	
	

	
	









	
	

	

	
